welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Maywood, a charming city known for its historic sites and friendly locals. Get ready to explore and experience all the beauty and culture this city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whiteman Airport serves as the primary hub for all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Whiteman Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing convenient services and amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Gates 1-10

terminals.name: Gates 11-20

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 2 hours.
